Name: MAXIMUM LOAD LENGTH IN METRES
Explanation: THE MAXIMUM LINEAR METERAGE THAT MAY BE CARRIED BY THE LANDING CRAFT.

Name: DROP ZONE LENGTH IN METRES
Explanation: THE DISTANCE MEASURED FROM THE LEADING EDGE OF THE DROP ZONE ALONG THE AIRCRAFT'S FLIGHT PATH TO THE TRAILING EDGE OF THE DROP ZONE.

Name: LENGTH OF LONGEST SPAN IN METRES
LANDING SITE LENGTH IN METRES
Explanation: THE DISTANCE MEASURED FROM THE LEADING EDGE OF THE LANDING SITE ALONG THE AIRCRAFT'S FLIGHT PATH TO THE TRAILING EDGE OF THE LANDING SITE.

Name: OVERALL LENGTH IN METRES, 1-99.99
Explanation: GIVES THE MEASUREMENT OF THE OVERALL LENGTH IN METERS. TWO DECIMAL PLACES ARE PERMITTED.

Name: LENGTH IN LANE METRES, 1 - 9999
Explanation: LENGTH NEEDED TO TRANSPORT VEHICLES ON SHIP.
